The '''Barotac Nuevo Plaza Field''' is a football venue in [[Barotac Nuevo]], Iloilo. The field is located at the town plaza.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bello|first1=Omar|title=FITNESS No-nonsense Caligdong recalls how Barotac days shaped him as a player and person|url=http://www.spin.ph/sports/fitness/mens-health/no-nonsense-caligdong-recalls-how-barotac-days-shaped-him-as-a-player-and-person|accessdate=26 March 2015|publisher=Sports Interactive Network Philippines|date=18 September 2013}}</ref> The football field was one of the two venues of the [[2008 AFC Challenge Cup qualification|2008 AFC Challenge Cup qualifiers]] held in the Philippines along with the [[Iloilo Sports Complex]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Philippines Fail to Qualify for AFC Challenge Cup|url=http://www.aseanfootball.org/v2/?p=5881|accessdate=26 March 2015|publisher=ASEAN Football Federatiin|date=18 May 2008|location=lloilo City}}</ref>

